node_2.subject: Emerald Puyor
node_2.description: This is Emerald Puyor's plan for Tuesday February 14: wake up and complete the morning routine at 5:00 am, open Puyor's Store at 7:00 am, serve customers from 7:00 am to 12:00 pm, have a lunch break from 12:00 pm to 1:00 pm, resume service from 1:00 pm to 7:00 pm, close the store at 7:00 pm, review the day and plan for tomorrow at 8:00 pm, watch TV from 7 to 8 pm.
